{"title":"为和平祈祷","authors":["玛哈蒙迪·穆尼拉"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":12,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"为和平祈祷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰国  玛哈蒙迪·穆尼拉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让和平之树结满硕果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的信念坚定不移；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻求通往和平之路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我愿为此奋斗不息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿人人领悟和平真谛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让称霸者住手；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战火熄灭，战魔绝迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿世界大同，人人亲亲密密。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿人人和睦相处似蜜蜂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互谅、互让又团结；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来灿烂未来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢与美好天堂相比。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜜蜂采蜜靠团结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫和平靠友谊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"携手前进众心齐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争得和平甜胜蜜。（邱苏瑾　陈安译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}